<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/59355772-br-der---bestien---automaten"><img alt="Brüder - Bestien - Automaten: Das Tier im abendländischen Denken" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1634341357l/59355772._SY75_.jpg" />
