<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/59355821-das-seufzende-schwein"><img alt="Das seufzende Schwein: Zur Theorie und Praxis in deutschen Modellen zur Tierethik" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1634342194l/59355821._SX50_.jpg" />
